[PAPA SHIROGANE inhales]

00:20:07.290 --> 00:20:09.668 position:50% align:center
The thing I don't know
is what he means to you,

00:20:09.751 --> 00:20:11.628 position:50% align:center
Kaguya Shinomiya.

00:20:11.711 --> 00:20:15.715 position:50% align:center
Is our relationship
significant somehow?

00:20:17.217 --> 00:20:18.718 position:50% align:center
Way back,

00:20:18.802 --> 00:20:22.263 position:50% align:center
I used to think there weren't
any good people in this world

00:20:22.347 --> 00:20:25.058 position:50% align:center
