00:21:10.186 --> 00:21:12.647 position:50% align:center
Well, you've made me
genuinely curious.

00:21:12.731 --> 00:21:15.233 position:50% align:center
Love 'im or leave 'im,
it isn't that hard.

00:21:15.316 --> 00:21:18.403 position:50% align:center
