00:21:35.628 --> 00:21:37.714 position:50% align:center
President.

00:21:37.797 --> 00:21:40.216 position:50% align:center
So do you know this gentleman?

00:21:40.300 --> 00:21:43.053 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Well, uh...

00:21:43.136 --> 00:21:44.637 position:50% align:center
First I've ever seen him.

00:21:44.721 --> 00:21:47.849 position:50% align:center
