00:21:47.932 --> 00:21:49.976 position:50% align:center
[screams]

00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:52.395 position:50% align:center
You knew who I was the
whole time, didn't you?

00:21:52.479 --> 00:21:53.646 position:50% align:center
Bingo, cupcake.

00:21:53.730 --> 00:21:55.982 position:50% align:center
How fun.

00:21:56.066 --> 00:21:57.317 position:50% align:center
Who would've guessed
that your father

00:21:57.400 --> 00:21:59.069 position:50% align:center
