00:21:59.152 --> 00:22:00.779 position:50% align:center
Yeah...

00:22:00.862 --> 00:22:03.073 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Old man!

00:22:03.156 --> 00:22:07.535 position:50% align:center
